42.49 0 M (work on the fiddle.  Another interesting thing is that she switches between A dorian)show
0 -12.10 T
42.49 0 M (\(with a C natural\) - which seems to be the standard - and mixolydian \(C sharp\).  She combines)show
0 -12.10 T
